it.emarolab.scene_identification_tagging

Interface SITBase.INDIVIDUAL

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    Enclosing interface:
    SITBase

    public static interface SITBase.INDIVIDUAL
extends SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    The interface containing all the constants related to individuals.

    This interface is aimed to be a container for all the String constants used in the ontology for addressing individuals.

    File: it.emarolab.scene_identification_tagging.SITBase

    date: 05/06/17
